name: Walk Thru The Eye
description:
Hi I am Lewis, a 14 year old game developer from New Zealand who just finish his first game jam. I've joined the Frightfully funky jam which is an small jam that lasts about an week. Due too not having enough time I couldn't finish the game and restriction making unplayable for gamepad.

This game is inspired by the backrooms and liminal spaces.
